Monaca for Visual Studio
==============================

Monaca for Visual Studio is an Visual Studio extension which provides the posiibility to Monaca users to develop an app using Microsoft Visual Studion IDE. It allows to make the development localy by benefiting the funtionalities of Visual Studio. Furthermore, the local developed project is seamlessly synchronized with the Monaca Cloud IDE. 

